text: My favourite parking place when visiting ICA is at here. There are many food stalls here when passing by and I managed to try one by one stalls here from subway, burger kings, etc. There is one coffee shop here. The complex has 2 blocks and there is a bridge connecting them both.
Quite a few eateries here but no much stores to shop for. You can visit XM studio at the highest level where there is an impressive display of Marvel, DC, etc... figurines.

Marvel fans got to visit XM at level 3, plentiful of models for photo taking. Understand from shop owner, they are the flagship store for Marvel and models are all drawn and produced by base on their own artist .

Located not far from V hotel lavender just a short walk  after the building across V hotel. Many variery of food and drinks and some is halal/kosher and some is not. Price is moderate but still affordable.
